      "span_text": "In son feedback mechanism yielded only a modest effect on practice patterns, and the potential cost-savings from changes in physician behavior did not always outweigh the cost of providing the feedback. Limited research has been published on the sole impact of physician profiles or the combined effect of physician profiles and academic detailing on prescribing habits and practice patterns."
